schools.name: William J Montford Iii Middle School

data.description: Charming pool home in Killearn Estates . This house has 3 large bedrooms, with LVP recently installed throughout the house, perfect for kids and pets. It's located on a quiet street in a great neighborhood, just a short walk from Roberts Elementary and Montford Middle School. The home has a large 2 car garage and indoor laundry room, which could be used as an office or great drop zone. Pool comes with a great cover for cold months and the sellers are offering to pay for professional pool care through the end of 2024.
